content: NOTE: FileProtect is a Java program and may be saved as a Java archive (.JAR file), with the name FileProtect.jar. It is designed for mobile phones, but may also run on computers with Java installed.

description: File encrypted with FileProtect, an encryption program for smartphones and other mobile devices; saved in a secure format that can only be opened after decrypting the file with FileProtect.
